{"tid":1486533,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[最幾重要] Set死線， 23 號點睇。","createTime":"2019-08-19T01:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T16:44:12.000Z","uid":148709,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"be43b237409339c1b145d643acb855c1b52fd05f","tid":1486533,"uid":148709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:56:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多謝各位示威同志琴日嘅170 萬人，贏曬我啲眼淚。可惜政府咁講：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4cNDPzJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4cNDPzJ.jpg&h=8ffad642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道有人想用黎賭美國9月5 會救香港，但係可惜我記得<span style=\"color: red;\">G20都係咁講。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以我想回歸初心，<span style=\"color: red;\">訂立升級死線</span>，最好就<span style=\"color: red;\">22 號</span>政府要答應我地。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係我地就升級<span style=\"color: navy;\">和平迫爆機場</span>，或者 <span style=\"color: red;\">出力參觀特首辦</span>，或者 <span style=\"color: violet;\">Summer On Fire皇后像廣場</span>，或者<span style=\"color: red;\">罷工塞鐵</span>咩都好。</span>"},{"pid":"2af3cda89dae71a29dbc4b3372c117c9f055f71e","tid":1486533,"uid":1751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:56:50.000Z","msg":"help push"},{"pid":"5f7fc021caf02050aefe7d2f34c28faac5a618ad","tid":1486533,"uid":213379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:58:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n820 死線<br />\n<br />\n823人鏈<br />\n<br />\n824 機場<br />\n<br />\n824 觀塘<br />\n<br />\n825 荃葵青<br />\n<br />\n831 中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n9月三罷<br />\n<br />\n不分和勇！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"eb7622ec9b2a748b6a36471eab290e9c0dcae8e0","tid":1486533,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:58:33.000Z","msg":"Set Deadline,  不分化，唔理勇唔勇武，和理非可以繼續做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://g2.dcdn.lt/images/pix/baltijos-kelias-v-cepliausko-nuotr-65429744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg2.dcdn.lt%2Fimages%2Fpix%2Fbaltijos-kelias-v-cepliausko-nuotr-65429744.jpg&h=6678ec11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">8月23日 人鏈：香港之路Hong Kong Way正！式！上！線！！！！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正式名稱：香港之路 The Hong Kong Way<br />\n日期：２０１９年８月２３日（星期五）<br />\n集合地點：港島線及荃灣觀塘線沿線各港鐵站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路線圖 (細節待定)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOnPTuT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOnPTuT.jpg&h=f65321a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大致分三段：<br />\n港島線（筲箕灣 &mdash; 堅尼地城）：13KM<br />\n荃灣線（黃埔 &mdash; 美孚）：7.02KM<br />\n觀塘線（深水埗 &mdash; 油塘）：12.6KM<br />\n<br />\n時序：<br />\n集合並在行人路上排隊 19:15-20:00<br />\n手牽手組人鏈 20:00-21:00<br />\n和平散去 21:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">快啲幫手開post宣傳<br />\n 整文宣！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22c2e3d905b6aa6bfa54fc4cb62544b0a6d1ecb","tid":1486533,"uid":148709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"自up"},{"pid":"51e5aa3b5a22a3e37441eacdfad26fdb477837a1","tid":1486533,"uid":79039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分勇和 手足齊心<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n因果由果 容港治己<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"d413d2297c3a838c38603aeff754980bc91682fc","tid":1486533,"uid":268569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:01:45.000Z","msg":"多謝手足提出咗我想講嘅嘢<br />\nbtw 和理非可唔可以唔好再捉鬼 行近水馬望入面狗隻部署情況 你就攞電筒雷射筆照我哋<br />\n照你老母閪咩 講撚咗喺中學生都仲照"},{"pid":"2b27e13408f3035436eded3e05a55b375bd0ea5f","tid":1486533,"uid":148709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:24:09.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"96db968554fc2a71ab845b084c420489e2d25162","tid":1486533,"uid":121855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:44:12.000Z","msg":"我永遠唔會贊成等人哋國家做野<br />\n人哋係根據我哋行動而作出回應"}]}